text: Parore or Paraore is a type of marine fish found around Australia and New Zealand. Parore is also a Māori personal or family name, and may refer to: *Adam Parore (born 1971), New Zealand cricketer *Louis Parore (1888–1953), Māori leader *Parore Te Awha (?–1887), Māori leader It may also refer to Te Pā A Parore, a marae and meeting house in Awanui, Northland Region, New Zealand
title: Parore (disambiguation)
